<span class="header1">Business/Management paired with Technology (CF)</span>

<p>With an "CF" interest, you will be a valuable employee. You like working with people on projects or assignments that have to do with biotechnology, information systems, engineering and environmental in the technology industries. The field of business is becoming more technical and fast-paced. This means that you will have many opportunities to find the occupation that suits you. You will be happiest in an occupation that allows you to use your ability to understand how things work and gives you a chance to make important transactions.</p>
<p>Many of the occupations in this pairing require some sort of specialized and/or technical training after high school. Some require college degrees or college level courses.</p>

